    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Reloadian 是一款快节奏动作游戏，专注于激烈战斗与自由构筑的探索体验。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败遍布宇宙的强大首领，每一次胜利都将解锁隐藏其中的传奇武器与能力。每场战斗都会带来全新的选择，鼓励你尝试不同的玩法风格，发现强力组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以独自作战，或与队友合作，在协作模式中配合与时机决定生存。适应源源不断的敌人，掌握流畅的移动方式，将战斗技巧推向极限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借风格化的动作表现、高重玩性的流程以及跨平台联机，Reloadian 挑战你开辟自己的道路，定义你的战斗方式。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>三人合作动作玩法</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125690/extras/1d88d48a033d426058941a562e5b699d.poster.avif?t=1772179608\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125690/extras/1d88d48a033d426058941a562e5b699d.webm?t=1772179608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125690/extras/1d88d48a033d426058941a562e5b699d.mp4?t=1772179608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>残酷的首领战</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125690/extras/1c5fe0cd2c5a3133ba5d3ba68642404a.poster.avif?t=1772179608\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125690/extras/1c5fe0cd2c5a3133ba5d3ba68642404a.webm?t=1772179608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125690/extras/1c5fe0cd2c5a3133ba5d3ba68642404a.mp4?t=1772179608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>每次流程，全新构筑</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.